cat << EOF
Warning! This revision introduces breaking changes from Gobo 017.01 to 
Gobo 017.01-r1.

The ESP's mount point has been moved from /System/Kernel/Boot/efi to
/System/Kernel/ESP. 

The grub boot-directory too has been moved from /System/Kernel/Boot/grub
into the ESP partition at /System/Kernel/ESP/grub. This includes grub.cfg,
themes, fonts, locales etc.

Legacy BIOS booting is unaffected.
EOF
